title: Mayday.Air.Crash.Investigations.S06.E03.Special.Who's.Flying.the
description:
Who's Flying the Plane



Aired on 03/02/2008, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



(the third of three special episodes airing between Seasons 4 and 5, listed as season 6 on the DVD set)

This special looked at accidents and incidents where problems with the interface between crew members and onboard avionics were a major factor to consider, and the causes of those problems.
